// return the old ones as an array of Float32Array:
//	[0]: index of the note in the ABC source
//	[1]: time in seconds
//	[2]: MIDI instrument (MIDI GM number - 1)
//	[3]: MIDI note pitch (with cents)
//	[4]: duration
//	[5]: volume (0..1)
//	[6]: voice number
